OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman stabbed to death in Birmingham
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a man was stabbed to
OL,8,Fdeath in Birmingham yesterday evening
OL,9,F(Thursday 4 June).
OL,11,FPolice were called to Walford Road in
OL,12,FSparkbrook at around 6:20pm after a
OL,13,Fman, believed to be in his 40s, was
OL,14,Fattacked.
OL,16,FHe was pronounced dead at around 7pm.
OL,18,FNo arrests have yet been made and
OL,19,Fofficers are currently appealing for
OL,20,Fany witnesses in the area to get in
OL,21,Ftouch.
